tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE ai_model_configurations (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    model_name VARCHAR(255),
    model_type VARCHAR(50),
    configuration JSON,
    parameters JSON
)

CREATE TABLE ai_model_configs (
  model_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  model_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  model_description TEXT,
  created_at TIMESTAMP NOT NULL
)

CREATE TABLE ai_model_parameters (
  parameter_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  model_id UUID REFERENCES ai_model_configs(model_id),
  parameter_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  parameter_value FLOAT NOT NULL
)

CREATE TABLE model_metadata (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    model_id INT,
    training_data_source VARCHAR(255),
    validation_data_source VARCHAR(255),
    test_data_source VARCHAR(255)
);
